  "text": "• Part-of-Speech Features (POS): Similar to the BoE feature set, this feature set aims to capture some generalisation patterns for the words. For this reason, the syntactical patterns within the documents are considered and used to extend the lexical BoW features. In light of our previous work [CITATION_1] , we used Ritter et al.'s Twitter NLP Tool; this POS tagger has been trained on short text messages. For each POS tag again the TF-IDF weighting was assigned.",
